HEADWORD: Bubalus
<hw>Bubalus</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a genus of ruminants which in some
classification systems is included in the genus <gen>Bos</gen>; the
water buffaloes.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> genus <gen>Bubalus</gen>, tribe Bubalus.</syn>⟦br⟧
